item.title: Error
item.dc:creator: @Yz85Racer Yz85Racer
item.description:
@Yz85Racer wrote:

Err. By the looks of the code you’re trying to invoke a method in java.lang.String called length(). There’s no method for such a thing, as it is a Field in java.lang.String.

Instead of doing Integer.toString(food).length(), do Integer.toString(food).length
